address2: 16th Floor, Room 1601-05 No.100 Zunyi Road Changning District
longBusinessSummary: Shanghai XNG Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, operates a chain of restaurants in Mainland China and Hong Kong. The company operates 31 Shanghai Min restaurants, one Maison DeL'Hui restaurants, four The Dining Room restaurants, one Oreno restaurant, and one Wolfgang Puck restaurant. It is also involved in the management of restaurants; provision of management, as well as IT technology services; franchise operation; and sale of software. The company was formerly known as TANSH Global Food Group Co., Ltd and changed its name to Shanghai XNG Holdings Limited in March 2022. Shanghai XNG Holdings Limited was founded in 1987 and is headquartered in Shanghai, the People's Republic of China.
